$section cppad_swig: A C++ Object Library and Swig Interface to Cppad$$

$head Goal$$
Provide a link from any scripting language supported by
$href%http://www.Swig.org%Swig%$$
to the
$href%https://www.coin-or.org/Cppad%Cppad%$$
algorithmic differentiation package.
In addition, the C++ library that does the computations is specified
and can be linked directly by other programs (besides Swig wrappers).

$head Under Construction$$
This is a preliminary version of $code cppad_swig$$.
Only a few AD functions have been implemented and are being used
for initial testing.
The currently working scripting languages, operating systems are:
$table
Python $cnext Linux, msys $rnext
Octave $cnext Linux $rnext
Perl   $cnext Linux
$tend
Only testing, and no installation, is currently implemented.

