$head Testing$$
You must first configure cppad_swig for your system using
$cref run_cmake.sh$$.
When you do so, the set of available tests would be output
as messages of the form
$codei%
	make check_%test_name%: available
%$$
You can change into the $code build$$ subdirectory and enter the command
$codei%
	make check_%test_name%
%$$
for each such test.

